程序包 org.springframework.cglib.proxy

Spring's repackaging of the CGLIB proxy package (for internal use only).

请参阅: 说明

  • 接口概要 
    接口 说明
    Enhancer.EnhancerKey
    Internal interface, only public due to ClassLoader issues.
  • 类概要 
    类 说明
    Enhancer
    Generates dynamic subclasses to enable method interception.
    MethodProxy
    Classes generated by Enhancer pass this object to the registered MethodInterceptor objects when an intercepted method is invoked.

程序包org.springframework.cglib.proxy的说明

Spring's repackaging of the CGLIB proxy package (for internal use only).

As this repackaging happens at the class file level, sources and javadocs are not available here... except for a few files that have been patched for Spring's purposes on JDK 9/10/11.
